    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable per ASME V&V 40 at MRL 2 given the medium model influence and high decision consequence classification. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 10) is met across all evaluated operating conditions, and the overall evidence package supports regulatory submission.",
